---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="What Northville Tech collects, stores, and shares — and what we don't."
>
  <div class="container-prose" style="padding: 3rem 0;">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="small">Last updated April 2026.</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> anonymized page views and basic device info via privacy-respecting analytics. No individual user tracking beyond what's needed to measure traffic.</li>
      <li><strong>Email list (opt-in only):</strong> your email address if you subscribe to our newsletter, stored with our email provider (Kit / ConvertKit). You can unsubscribe with one click in any email.</li>
      <li><strong>Affiliate clicks:</strong> when you click an affiliate link, the merchant's network (Impact, CJ, Amazon, etc.) may drop a cookie. We don't see who you are — only that a click was attributed to us.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What we don't collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We don't sell your data. Ever</li>
      <li>We don't run third-party ad networks (no banners, no retargeting pixels).</li>
      <li>We don't track you across the web.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      This site uses minimal first-party cookies for basic session handling. Affiliate links may set
      third-party cookies from the merchant's network — these are used for commission attribution only.
      You can clear them anytime.
    </p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      If you're in the EU, UK, or California, you have the right to request access to, correction of,
      or deletion of any personal data we hold about you. Email{' '}
      <a href="mailto:hello@northvilletech.com">hello@northvilletech.com</a> to make a request and we
      will respond within 30 days.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Privacy questions: <a href="mailto:hello@northvilletech.com">hello@northvilletech.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
